title: Flight Simulator 2020 - How to - ATR 42 600/72 600 - Using the autopilot
description:
In this video we will look at how to use the autopilot in the ATR 42-600/72-600. We will go through the individual options which are available in the autopilot. Once we are airborne we will use several of the functionalities to see how they can help you during your flight.
